        "594d259f-babe-4683-bb1d-44d88ad96f34": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "3. Peel Hot After a Few Seconds",
            "title_size": "heading-size--small",
            "seo_h_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "e7c2c918-9986-4016-9fab-ac17c4e87b3b": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With our proprietary Ninja Peel Technology, you can peel hot or cool. Wait a few seconds (or more) and peel! If parts of the design are not sticking, lay it back down and press again with added pressure and heat (+15°F).  If unsuccessful, increase heat by 15°F increments until it works. Remember, the great thing about NinjaTransfers is that repeated pressing won't damage the transfer.</p>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
